-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #2f3a8e; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #333399;\">Duraci&oacute;n: 5-8 horas.</span></strong></li>\n</ul>','1646275561.png','1','2022-03-03 08:46:01','2022-03-17 21:12:48');
